Package: noaa.visualise
Type: Package
Title: NOAA Earthquakes Processing and Visualising
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Anh", "Dang", email = "maianhdang.ftu@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Anh Dang <maianhdang.ftu@gmail.com>
Description: The package is to process and visualize the NOAA dataset about earthquakes.
    The visualisation includes: 
    i) Plotting earthquakes in timeline; 
    ii) Interactive leaflet with locations of earthquakes in maps 
